ActCanada Grain Act
PrecisAppointment of ANTHONY DOUGLAS CHORNEY of East Selkirk, Manitoba, to be a Commissioner of the Canadian Grain Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years; and his designation as Chief Commissioner of the Canadian Grain Commission.
